{"tid":635451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共分枝伸入美校園？傳中國交換生在美大學組「臨時黨支部」","createTime":"2018-04-20T06:43:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-21T08:44:26.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"8338671c91c5ce3aafa7592e6be6a7bd88aca288","tid":635451,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T06:43:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/20/144215_fa284a98af525ca986abaa65d4c9e3bb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F20%2F144215_fa284a98af525ca986abaa65d4c9e3bb.png&h=12657c93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n伊利諾大學厄巴納-香檳分校（University of Illinois at Urbana-Champaign ，UIUC）的中國華中科技大學交換學生，在該校組織中共「臨時黨支部」。（圖片擷取自《外交政策》網站）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國多所大學被發現，有中國交換學生在校內組織「臨時黨支部」，並藉此監控中國學生是否有「反中國」言行。<br />\n<br />\n《外交政策》（Foreign Policy）雜誌18日刊登文章指出，美國各州大學皆出現由中國交換學生組織的「臨時黨支部」（temporary party branch ）。報導中舉出，2017年伊利諾大學厄巴納-香檳分校（University of Illinois at Urbana-Champaign ，UIUC），有9位中國華中科技大學的交換學生，在該校組織了中共「臨時黨支部」。<br />\n<br />\nUIUC「臨時黨支部」會安排學生觀看中共十九大影片，並要黨支部成員回報其他中國同學是否有反黨言行。有中國交換生表示，在赴美前，原就讀大學會要求學生不得參加美國的法輪功聚會。<br />\n<br />\n中官媒《環球時報》也曾報導，這些海外「臨時黨支部」的任務包括「推動黨和政府的政策」。<br />\n<br />\nUIUC公共事務辦公室則拒絕回應，是否知情校園內有中共黨分支，並稱「我們確保中國交換學生，有機會自由追求UIUC提供的教育體驗」。<br />\n<br />\n《外交政策》文章中稱，這些「臨時黨支部」在交換學生們返回中國後就會解散。而除了伊利諾州，加州、紐約州、康乃迪克州、北達科他等洲的大學，甚至歐洲、亞洲國家校園也出現過「臨時黨支部」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2401306\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2401306&d=NITwp9Q6aaCxncUz4%2BDeoP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=a2458eae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2401306&h=691ff9dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2401306</a>"},{"pid":"dcc981aed32e7d3e132e2174c175f5b8bcaed289","tid":635451,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T06:44:56.000Z","msg":"滲透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7500c78e57cafb33ee68713a6160f9c2d9fdeaa8","tid":635451,"uid":45518,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T06:46:19.000Z","msg":"咁做只會令美國更大力打壓返中國"},{"pid":"c226e17badd2e6a7b3492a01fc9c0e2d1fd3fc34","tid":635451,"uid":87723,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T06:47:12.000Z","msg":"留名睇ban埋留學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e959d25c688f477016ff90a65384ca40d6ac1df3","tid":635451,"uid":3241,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T06:47:44.000Z","msg":"即時驅逐出境啦呢班垃圾"},{"pid":"650f2d23addef6a96c177b9eb4afd1202385d0ab","tid":635451,"uid":66496,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T06:49:25.000Z","msg":"侵侵地頭玩嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nOn9中國人係咪以為自己大撚晒"},{"pid":"3478793bd203dcdf88857f850a343ab856fcf745","tid":635451,"uid":34103,"like":1,"dislike":20,"score":-19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T06:49:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6bbdaa56db7a98abd18ab0b0055e1ddeb390370e","tid":635451,"uid":67468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T06:50:01.000Z","msg":"完"},{"pid":"7f671dec6fed669337c96e57f1b39e779d2e26a2","tid":635451,"uid":4783,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T06:51:24.000Z","msg":"組織黨支部係政治工作黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去讀書應該係study visa<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 全部都可以被驅逐出境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果認定係間諜